    <p>Individual form controls automatically receive some global styling. By default, <code>&lt;input&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code>, and <code>&lt;select&gt;</code> elements with <code>.form-control</code> are set to a recommended width of 296px by setting <code>max-width: 296px</code>. Wrap labels and controls in <code>.form-group</code> for optimum spacing.
